; 06:00 daily — ahead of the 07:25/07:30 morning runs so balances are fresh for
; the M6.3 finance consumers (the weekly-briefing Money section + dashboard
; drawer + the >35d stale-import line; those go live at M6.3 — SPEC §12.2). The
; 07:25 engine + 07:30 digest do not read finance. Cadence is the first tuning
; knob: if Max/Cal OTP re-challenges prove noisy, drop the cards to 2–3×/week.
[Unit]
Description=Family inc. finance scraper timer (06:00 Asia/Jerusalem)

[Timer]
OnCalendar=*-*-* 06:00:00
Persistent=true
AccuracySec=1m

[Install]
WantedBy=timers.target
